            The digital single-issue versions for the entire series were collected
            by  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/user/blackcanary" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/user/blackcanary</a>   here:

              <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8757378" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8757378</a>

            Those releases are mostly in hi-res already, but have several "lo-res
            gaps" in the early part of the run (#1-8 and #15-16, according to my
            notes). Between them, this release of book one, and the release of book
            two posted by  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/user/nemesis43" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/user/nemesis43</a>   earlier,

              <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9708990" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9708990</a>

            plug those, which means that anyone who doesn't mind mixing the two
            formats now has access to everything at top quality! For purists who
            like to keep the formats separate, I'm sure the remaining collected
            editions will be along in due course, though. :)
